A FUR está vindo!

182
00:18:49,409 --> 00:18:51,662
FUR! FUR! FUR!

183
00:18:51,912 --> 00:18:54,289
FUR! FUR! FUR!

184
00:18:54,581 --> 00:18:57,292
FUR! FUR! FUR!

185
00:18:57,417 --> 00:18:59,920
FUR! FUR! FUR!

186
00:19:05,592 --> 00:19:07,219
Ei!

187
00:19:07,678 --> 00:19:09,596
